'''Packet Tracer'''是由[[思科系统|思科系统]]设计的[[跨平臺|跨平台]]可视化[[仿真|仿真]]工具，它允许用户创建[[网络拓扑|网络拓扑]]以模仿[[计算机网络|计算机网络]]和使用命令行界面來模拟配置思科路由器和交换机。Packet Tracer的用户界面為拖放式，允许用户根据自己的需要添加和删除模拟的网络设备。该软件主要面向參加[[思科认证网络工程师|思科认证网络工程师]]認證考試的学生，作为他们備考[[思科认证网络工程师|思科认证网络工程师]]認證考試的學習工具<ref name="jar">{{cite journal |url=http://www.ijarcce.com/upload/2014/may/IJARCCE3F%20%20a%20sheikh%20Role%20of%20Packet%20Tracer%20in.pdf |title=Role of Packet Tracer in learning Computer Networks |first1=Sheikh Raashid |last1=Javid |journal=International Journal of Advanced Research in Computer and Communication Engineering |volume=3 |issue=5 |date=2014-05 |pages=6508–6511 |access-date=2020-09-18 |archive-date=2020-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610210649/https://www.ijarcce.com/upload/2014/may/IJARCCE3F%20%20a%20sheikh%20Role%20of%20Packet%20Tracer%20in.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="JOU-1"/>。

